{"tid":2047377,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"眾志三成員襲擊案 官質疑保安口供","createTime":"2020-06-02T05:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T05:27:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"015c339c5f4ff9cd3f6a56bf5ae663ae6be9aeff","tid":2047377,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200602/PBSKEQCNDBVUWZPWBP4XEY23FI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FPBSKEQCNDBVUWZPWBP4XEY23FI%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbWztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=3f381339\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FPBSKEQCNDBVUWZPWBP4XEY23FI%2F&h=45d48b3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200602/PBSKEQCNDBVUWZPWBP4XEY23FI/</a><br />\n<br />\n眾志三成員襲擊案 官質疑保安口供<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y3VFCI3EHZCGEKSMT5LBNB7QAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY3VFCI3EHZCGEKSMT5LBNB7QAI.jpg&h=c8940034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭家朗及吳嘉兒否認在立法會內不守秩序。 朱永倫攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港眾志。。。。。。。。。。高度不同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZQX7AC5O5MYBG7SJPZALELMJVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZQX7AC5O5MYBG7SJPZALELMJVM.jpg&h=97ec8c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「膊頭根本唔同水平」<br />\n<br />\n被告鄭家朗（20歲）、吳嘉兒（21歲）、何秀儀（21歲）各被票控一項在立法會會議廳範圍內逗留時未有遵守秩序罪，何另涉襲擊保安員許耀德，各罪指被告去年3月16日在立法會綜合大樓2樓的1號會議室犯案。一級保安助理許耀德作供指，鄭家朗完成發言後，拿出小型擴音器並離開座位，吳與何亦從座位衝出來。他張開雙臂嘗試阻擋何，但何不理，更「衝力太大」把他撞跌。他稱何的左膊撞到他的左膊，他倒地後痛到不能站起。<br />\n<br />\n控方多次播放事發經過片段，許未能指出膊頭何時遇襲，裁判官何俊堯看片後更指，看不到兩人膊頭有接觸，「（被告）個膊頭從來都遠離你左邊，佢個膊頭根本同你都唔同水平」。許看片後同意。許亦稱，沒印象何有否接觸他其他身體部位，又稱肩膊至手肘部位痛到不能動彈，辯方播放其他片段顯示許可以擺動及屈曲左臂，許看片後同意說法。<br />\n<br />\n攔截。。。。。。。。。警覺。<br />\n<br />\n女高。。。。。。。。。。陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2312、ESS33914-16/19<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"bdd9d262be7c80aa2287c04ef2f229830f2976df","tid":2047377,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"個保安係咪又係嗰啲退休狗<br />\n啲狗最鍾意比假口供喎"},{"pid":"ffe6d36a4bdb795b835581d017b87ae43aaeafac","tid":2047377,"uid":237487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"個個講美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人變condom"},{"pid":"7d1454eefc57da64f87849a8dffeb7f30cabc56b","tid":2047377,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"班官開始驚制裁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1601b6776a36da4338134a2bfe63e9e2761d1c31","tid":2047377,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"要反告佢比假証供"},{"pid":"4d56a2a44c1a94c75991386cb76e2f12fb3502f5","tid":2047377,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"最近的case全部都係濫告"},{"pid":"8d4ff12182c72b6103d9eca86f3ef1d426c7c7a9","tid":2047377,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"姐係許曱甴俾假口供？"},{"pid":"9132cde9512355b1c747c3c51cdf5eec83176242","tid":2047377,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d4ff12182c72b6103d9eca86f3ef1d426c7c7a9","tid":2047377,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"姐係許曱甴俾假口供？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:27:58.000Z","msg":"梁天琦生日快樂！一條片回顧天琦過去講過嘅金句<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2047363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2047363</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}